@database WindowClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Window Class"


Window class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "NotifyClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Window class is used to create Intuition windows.

  Note that:

     o Any window must be added to an application object to be
       opened

     o A window is not created if its Contents is not defined.

     o Any graphical object must be added to a window to be
     visible

  See @{"Application" LINK "ApplicationFunctions.guide/Main"}.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

