  @{fg shine}SetCycleChain@{fg text}
  {obj}
  Sets the window cycle chain to max 13 objects. If you have more
  than 13 objects in your cycle chain, you have to set
  Area/CycleChain attribute of each. Passing no object resets the
  cycle chain.

